Package: glanus-agent
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6, libssl3 | libssl1.1, libdbus-1-3, libsecret-1-0, libxdo3, libvpx7 | libvpx9 | libvpx6
Recommends: xdotool
Maintainer: Glanus <support@glanus.com>
Homepage: https://glanus.com
Description: Glanus RMM Agent (headless daemon)
 Cross-platform remote monitoring and management agent for Glanus RMM.
 On Linux the agent runs headlessly as a systemd service for background
 monitoring, remote script execution, and automatic updates.
